item.title: R.I.P Marco Simoncelli 1987-2011
item.description:
R.I.P Marco Simoncelli 1987-2011
Marco Simoncelli killed in at Malaysian Moto GP. Italian motorcyclist Marco Simoncelli has been killed in a crash during today's Malaysian Moto GP. The Gresini Honda rider lost control of his bike on the second lap of the circuit in Sepang and appeared to be hit by Colin Edwards and then Valentino Rossi as he slid across the track. The 24-year-old's helmet came off in the collision and he was taken to the medical centre for treatment, but his injuries were too serious. A message on the MotoGP website read: "Marco Simoncelli succumbed to injuries sustained in Malaysia." The organisers halted the race immediately after the incident, and then cancelled it. item.description:
Marco Simoncelli è morto.
Marco simoncelli è morto. Voleva vincere sulla pista di Sepang invece ha trovato le fine della sua vita. La sua moto è scivolata attraversando la pista e tagliando la strada a Bautista, Rossi e Edwards. Alvaro passa ma gli altri due lo centrano. Simoncelli viene colpito alla testa, il casco vola via e con esso la sua vita. RIP Simo.
